---

<Layout
  title="台灣前 50 大企業泡泡圖"
  description="以互動式 D3 泡泡圖呈現台灣前 50 大企業的市值、營收與產業分佈"
>
  <!--
    Phase 6 page migration #9: companies.astro
    ──────────────────────────────────────────
    - Scoped <style> removed entirely (~240 lines CSS deleted)
    - `.toggle-btn` / `.sector-btn` use [&.active]: arbitrary variants
      because the d3 script toggles the `.active` class as state
    - The D3-created `.tooltip` div was styled via `:global(.tooltip)`;
      instead of keeping the scoped hack, the script below now sets
      Tailwind utility classes directly on the created element
    - Per-row sector tag colors still flow through inline `style={}`
  -->
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-[var(--container-wide)] px-6 py-8">
    <div class="mb-8 text-center">
      <h1 class="mb-2 text-[2.2rem] max-[768px]:text-[1.6rem]">
        🏢 台灣前 50 大企業
      </h1>
      <p class="text-[1.1rem] leading-[1.6] text-[#555]">
        以市值為圓面積的互動泡泡圖，一目了然台灣產業版圖。<br />
        泡泡越大 = 市值越高，顏色代表產業，懸停查看詳情。
      </p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-[0.85rem] text-[#888]">
        📊 資料來源：TWSE、各公司年報、公開資訊觀測站（2025 年度近似值）<br />
        💡 點擊產業標籤可篩選；泡泡可拖曳
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-6 flex flex-col gap-4">
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2">
        <label class="text-[0.9rem] font-semibold">泡泡大小依據：</label>
        <button
          class="toggle-btn cursor-pointer rounded-[20px] border-2 border-[#ddd] bg-white px-4 py-[0.4rem] text-[0.85rem] transition-all duration-200 [&.active]:border-[#2563eb] [&.active]:bg-[#2563eb] [&.active]:text-white"
          data-mode="marketCap">市值</button
        >
        <button
          class="toggle-btn cursor-pointer rounded-[20px] border-2 border-[#ddd] bg-white px-4 py-[0.4rem] text-[0.85rem] transition-all duration-200 [&.active]:border-[#2563eb] [&.active]:bg-[#2563eb] [&.active]:text-white"
          data-mode="revenue">營收</button
        >
        <button
          class="toggle-btn cursor-pointer rounded-[20px] border-2 border-[#ddd] bg-white px-4 py-[0.4rem] text-[0.85rem] transition-all duration-200 [&.active]:border-[#2563eb] [&.active]:bg-[#2563eb] [&.active]:text-white"
          data-mode="employees">員工數</button
        >
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-[0.4rem]">
        <button
          class="sector-btn flex cursor-pointer items-center gap-[0.3rem] rounded-[15px] border border-[#ddd] bg-white px-[0.8rem] py-[0.3rem] text-[0.8rem] transition-all duration-200 [&.active]:border-[#999] [&.active]:bg-[#f0f0f0] [&.active]:font-semibold"
          data-sector="all">全部</button
        >
        {
          sectors.map((s) => (
            <button
              class="sector-btn flex cursor-pointer items-center gap-[0.3rem] rounded-[15px] border border-[#ddd] bg-white px-[0.8rem] py-[0.3rem] text-[0.8rem] transition-all duration-200 [&.active]:border-[#999] [&.active]:bg-[#f0f0f0] [&.active]:font-semibold"
              data-sector={s}
              style={`--sector-color: ${sectorColors[s] || '#888'}`}
            >
              <span
                class="inline-block h-2 w-2 rounded-full"
                style={`background: ${sectorColors[s] || '#888'}`}
              />
              {s}
            </button>
          ))
